snippet.title: (SPOILER) Amber Heard, Jason Momoa and James Wan talk Aquaman at the London press junket
snippet.description:
SPOILER WARNING | Jason, Amber and James talk Aquaman at the London press junket, in particular on the personal journey of Arthur to become king, Mera's character and the challenges of making this film.
